  <brief_title>S90652 in Paediatric Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety and Effects on Blood Pressure of Daily Dose 0.025 to 0.135 Milligram Per Kilogram of S90625 a Paediatric Formulation of Perindopril, in Hypertensive Children - 24 Months</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Institut de Recherches Internationales Servier</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Servier</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to assess the long-term safety and effects on blood pressure of a
      paediatric formulation of perindopril in hypertensive children
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
