  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Hypertensive children, who have been treated for four months at least with S90652,
             with safety and efficacy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Poorly controlled hypertension

          -  Girls with signs of pubescence
      </textblock>
